sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Device
    participant S as SQLite
    participant O as Outbox
    participant C as Cloud

    D->>S: Turn page (instant)
    D->>O: Queue progress update
    Note over O: Debounce timer<br/>collapses rapid turns

    O->>C: POST /api/v1/batch/reading-events
    C-->>O: Accepted (new version)

    Note over C: Another device<br/>pushes an update

    D->>C: GET /api/v1/sync/events?after=cursor
    C-->>D: New deltas from other devices
    D->>S: Apply after conflict check
